1
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:04,519
You're really keeping up the act, huh?

2
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,040
You were with Shen Qing,

3
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:08,560
and you didn't know she was pregnant?

4
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,760
Shen Qing was pregnant?

5
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:18,319
That's impossible.

6
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,280
She didn't tell you?

7
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,400
You're bluffing, aren't you?

8
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:33,200
Using tactics like this is downright despicable.

9
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:41,599
To the dead,

10
00:01:41,879 --> 00:01:43,120
it's highly disrespectful.

11
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,239
Take a look.

12
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,840
Don't dare to look?

13
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,599
You coward.

14
00:02:01,319 --> 00:02:03,480
This is what Shen Qing looked like when she died.

15
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:06,480
Open your eyes wide and look at her hands.

16
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:09,560
Look!

17
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:30,919
Do you understand what you're seeing?

18
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,840
Have you figured it out?

19
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,240
Want to know what she was doing?

20
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,400
This was her final act in life.

21
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,159
She used her last bit of strength

22
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,360
to raise both her hands.

23
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,319
For what?

24
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,400
To protect the baby in her womb.

25
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,680
Do you think a mother like that

26
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,400
would kill herself?

27
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,560
Take a good look for yourself.

28
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,759
According to our investigation,

29
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,599
you've been married for 20 years

30
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:19,960
with no children.

31
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,800
That's the main cause of your marital discord,

32
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:24,879
isn't it?

33
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,680
Enough. Stop talking.

34
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,960
I've seen a doctor.

35
00:03:37,639 --> 00:03:38,879
The doctor said

36
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,199
in my condition,

37
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,840
it's very hard to conceive a child.

38
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,439
Even if Shen Qing was pregnant,

39
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,599
how can you prove the child is mine?

40
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,840
Captain Li.

41
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,599
The paternity test results are in.

42
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,639
Chief Xing.

43
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,319
How's it going?

44
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,920
Looks like we can break him.

45
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,959
A son.

46
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,240
A son.

47
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,279
I had a son.

48
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,199
Are you happy?

49
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,399
If Shen Qing's death is linked to you,

50
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:22,000
then you killed your own child.

51
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,360
But if it was someone else,

52
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,360
then that someone

53
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:32,160
is the one who murdered your son.

54
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:37,040
I swear I never did anything to wrong you.

55
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,160
Take us away with you.

56
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:54,399
Why were you so foolish?

57
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:01,439
You were carrying our child.

58
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,800
Why didn't you tell me?

59
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,000
Why? Why?

60
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:20,959
You are so vicious.

61
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:26,079
You wouldn't even spare my son.

62
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,920
I'll make you all pay for this.

63
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:31,759
Who?

64
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,120
Who are you talking about?

65
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,319
The murderer.

66
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,120
Who is the murderer?

67
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,879
The murderer...

68
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,439
What are you hiding?

69
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,439
Su Zhuang.

70
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,639
Su Zhuang! Su Zhuang!

71
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,120
Li Kaiyang.

72
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,360
What were you thinking?

73
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,959
A routine interrogation, and you sent him to the hospital?

74
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:03,720
Chief Xing.

75
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,639
Li Kaiyang.

76
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,240
Su Zhuang is only a suspect.

77
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,040
He collapsed right under your watch.

78
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,519
This is no small matter.

79
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,480
I warned you before.

80
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,560
He's a bank president.

81
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,680
You needed to mind your methods when questioning him.

82
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,439
Do you know what could happen

83
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,839
if word of this gets out?

84
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:20,439
Chief Xing.

85
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,600
It was my line of questioning.

86
00:07:23,319 --> 00:07:24,240
It has nothing to do with Captain Li.

87
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,240
It's my fault.

88
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,639
I'll take full responsibility.

89
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,519
You're the head of the task force.

90
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,079
The responsibility falls on you.

91
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,160
Do you understand?

92
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,759
If anything happens to Su Zhuang,

93
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,240
can you bear the consequences?

94
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,600
As long as we catch the killer,

95
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,079
I'm willing to pay any price.

96
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,160
Still talking back?

97
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:42,079
Li Kaiyang.

98
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,240
I know

99
00:07:44,319 --> 00:07:47,000
you're highly experienced in solving cases and interrogating.

100
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,120
But this time,

101
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,360
your interrogation prep was inadequate.

102
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,399
Before questioning,

103
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:53,360
you should have made a thorough assessment

104
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,560
of the suspect's physical condition.

105
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,480
Understood?

106
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,600
It was my oversight.

107
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,160
I accept the criticism.

108
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:03,959
Doctor, how is he?

109
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:06,079
The patient suffered a severe shock,

110
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:08,079
causing an acute ischemic stroke.

111
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,399
After emergency treatment, he's out of danger.

112
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,680
With continued treatment, he should recover fully.

113
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:16,120
Good. Thank you.

114
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:16,720
Alright.

115
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,319
Stop right there.

116
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:21,959
Li Kaiyang.

117
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,839
You think the suspect wasn't shaken enough?

118
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,399
He is a criminal suspect.

119
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,240
Suspected of murder.

120
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,199
I have to monitor him.

121
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:27,920
Li Kaiyang.

122
00:08:28,639 --> 00:08:30,600
I'm hereby removing you as head of the task force.

123
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,759
The fall case will be handed to Wang Yonglin.

124
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:33,879
Chief Xing.

125
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:34,759
That's final.

126
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,360
Go back and reflect on this seriously.

127
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,399
Write a thorough self-criticism.

128
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:46,720
Let the patient recover slowly.

129
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:48,360
Once he's recovered,

130
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,039
then we'll resume the interrogation.

131
00:08:50,279 --> 00:08:50,879
Yes, sir.

132
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,320
Shifu.

133
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:58,360
Captain Wang's been away training all this time.

134
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,879
He doesn't know anything about this case.

135
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,960
Come on, Shifu.

136
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,919
This incident was just an accident.

137
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:05,840
Uncle Xing is being too unreasonable.

138
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:07,440
Removing you just like that.

139
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,480
"Uncle Xing"?

140
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:13,639
Oh, just a slip of the tongue.

141
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,879
I should've guessed you got in through connections.

142
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:20,639
Shifu, that's beneath you.

143
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,960
I joined the criminal squad on my own merit.

144
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,440
Chief Xing wanted me long ago.

145
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,840
If my dad hadn't objected...

146
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,039
Your dad?

147
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:28,399
Oh.

148
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:31,200
My dad and Chief Xing were colleagues before he retired.

149
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,320
Jiang...

150
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,480
Jiang Weimin.

151
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,000
Chief Jiang.

152
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:38,039
You know my dad?

153
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:45,399
Kid,

154
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:46,960
don't be afraid.

155
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:48,879
We're the police.

156
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,399
You have a good father.

157
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,440
He has a pair of warm hands.

158
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:57,799
Twenty-two years ago,

159
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,639
he was the one who pulled me back from hell.

160
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,799
The warmth of his hands,

161
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:04,639
I still remember it to this day.

162
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:09,120
You think more highly of my dad than I do.

163
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,679
Shifu.

164
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,000
I just don't understand.

165
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:15,559
What's your connection to that case 22 years ago?

166
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:19,840
Your dad knows all about that.

167
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:22,279
Find a time to sit down and have a good chat with him.

168
00:10:22,399 --> 00:10:23,720
Hey, hey, Shifu.

169
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:26,159
There's a rift between my dad and me.

170
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,279
If you don't want to talk about it,

171
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,519
then I won't ask.

172
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,360
I just feel it's unfair to you.

173
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,639
Was I kicked out of the major crimes unit?

174
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,600
Was I kicked off the task force?

175
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,200
So what's unfair about it?

176
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:46,159
It's better not being team leader.

177
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:48,919
More time to work the case.

178
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,919
To solve a case,

179
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,600
do we have to go through so many trials?

180
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,919
If life is like a string of prayer beads,

181
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,759
it's made up of one trial after another.

182
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:03,519
The harm and resistance you face

183
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,559
depends on the one turning the beads.

184
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:09,080
Profound, Shifu.

185
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,240
You're getting all philosophical.

186
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,440
Don't flatter me.

187
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,600
You stay here and keep watch.

188
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:17,600
Keep me updated on Su Zhuang's recovery.

189
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,080
I'm telling you,

190
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,720
no matter how much resistance this case faces,

191
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,080
I will get to the bottom of it.

192
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:26,559
Yes, sir.

193
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,279
It's settled.

194
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,200
Brother Li,

195
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:45,320
don't worry.

196
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:46,320
Once Ruolan moves in with me,

197
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,720
I'll take good care of her.

198
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:48,879
Safer than staying here.

199
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:50,799
Fair enough.

200
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:54,600
Staying at the nursing home isn't a long-term plan.

201
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:56,879
So you agree?

202
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,519
You two have already decided.

203
00:12:02,679 --> 00:12:03,799
What's there for me to disagree with?

204
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:07,919
But I have to warn you about one thing.

205
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,320
Ruolan is like my own sister.

206
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,159
If you dare mistreat her...

207
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,919
I... I'd mistreat myself

208
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:17,480
before I'd ever mistreat Ruolan.

209
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:20,960
Go pack your things.

210
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:22,240
I'll take you home.

211
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:23,000
Okay.

212
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,080
Easy now.

213
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,600
Come on.

214
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,000
A little further forward.

215
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,039
There we go.

216
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:46,200
Ruolan,

217
00:12:46,919 --> 00:12:48,440
this is going to be our new home from now on.

218
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,320
Look, a big balcony full of sunshine.

219
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:52,960
From now on, during the day,

220
00:12:53,399 --> 00:12:55,600
you can sit here drinking tea and reading,

221
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:56,919
soaking up the sun.

222
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:07,759
Thank you,

223
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:08,679
Mingliang.

224
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,000
I finally have a home again.

225
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:13,879
Oh, Ruolan,

226
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,120
I bought you a gift.

227
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:16,360
Quick, open it and see.

228
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,759
Wishing you good health,

229
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:25,919
and may you be safe forever.

230
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,960
And I hope our relationship

231
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,600
will always stay whole and happy.

232
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:35,279
I'd also like to invite Brother Li to share this apple.

233
00:13:35,519 --> 00:13:36,159
First,

234
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,240
as a witness to our love.

235
00:13:39,039 --> 00:13:40,799
Second, to thank you for taking care of her.

236
00:13:41,519 --> 00:13:42,840
And wishing you a swift rise in your career.

237
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:43,879
Mingliang,

238
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:45,519
I'll say it once more,

239
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,080
take good care of Ruolan.

240
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:48,639
If a single hair on her head is harmed,

241
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,080
I will not let you off the hook.

242
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,039
Don't worry, brother.

243
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,759
I will definitely take good care of Ruolan,

244
00:13:53,759 --> 00:13:54,840
and won't let her be harmed in the slightest.

245
00:13:58,559 --> 00:13:59,240
I'm heading out.

246
00:14:15,519 --> 00:14:16,279
Sorry,

247
00:14:16,799 --> 00:14:19,240
the number you dialed cannot be reached.

248
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:25,039
Here, have a bite.

249
00:14:29,399 --> 00:14:30,080
So sweet.

250
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,600
Just like our life together from now on.

251
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:36,799
Mingliang.

252
00:14:37,519 --> 00:14:39,120
Why is that room locked?

253
00:14:39,799 --> 00:14:40,279
Oh.

254
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:43,120
The landlord stored a lot of junk in there.

255
00:14:43,559 --> 00:14:45,080
The reason the rent is so cheap

256
00:14:45,519 --> 00:14:47,240
is because we can't use that room.

257
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:51,919
Ruolan.

258
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,519
Hmm?

259
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:54,600
It's your first day in my humble home.

260
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,559
What would you like for dinner?

261
00:14:58,279 --> 00:14:59,039
Hot pot.

262
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:21,799
My little princess,

263
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:24,799
wait for me at home.

264
00:15:25,519 --> 00:15:27,240
I'll go buy some hot pot base and be right back.

265
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,559
Welcome to your new home, darling.

266
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:41,839
Look.

267
00:17:42,559 --> 00:17:43,319
In here,

268
00:17:44,079 --> 00:17:45,200
every expression of yours,

269
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,319
every breath,

270
00:17:46,319 --> 00:17:47,480
every moment of fear,

271
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:48,640
every moment of sadness,

272
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:50,759
will all be recorded in full.

273
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,680
Where do you think you're running?

274
00:17:56,599 --> 00:17:58,039
If you don't behave,

275
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,559
I'll become your worst nightmare.

276
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,240
But if you're a good girl,

277
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:05,240
I'll treat you very well.

278
00:18:05,799 --> 00:18:06,440
Okay?

279
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,480
I'll be good.

280
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:09,960
That's more like it.

281
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:15,160
Come on, get up.

282
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,079
There's still time.

283
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:20,799
Let's play together for half an hour, okay?

284
00:18:21,359 --> 00:18:22,400
Wait.
